title: Ancient Traces: Mysteries in Ancient and Early History
description:
Ancient Traces: Mysteries in Ancient and Early History - Michael Baigent [epub]

In a series of different chapters Michael Baigent examines a number of enigmas surrounding such ancient mysteries as Atlantis and the Pyramids. He investigates such questions as whether there were ancient contacts between Europe and America,and whether a great catastrophe hit the planet around 10,000 BC. And in the process he calls into question much of today's orthodoxy on such subjects
